title: 79. Surviving The Success Zombie Apocalypse
itunes:title: 79. Surviving The Success Zombie Apocalypse
description: Are you someone who mindlessly consumes self-help knowledge with little to no action? Do you get comfortable after winning, or does it make you strive for more wins? On today's episode, Andy talks about how you have to get past the success zombie stage so you can fulfill your own true potential.
